# Maps

```scala
val m = Map("a" -> 1, "b" -> 2, "c" -> 3)
println(m.size)
println(m.getOrElse("a", 0))
println(m.contains("b"))
println(m.contains("z"))
println(m.getOrElse("c", 0))
println(m.getOrElse("z", 0))
val keys = m.keys.toList.sorted
println(keys.mkString(", "))
val vals = m.values.toList.sorted
println(vals.mkString(", "))
```
